From romain at r-enthusiasts.com  Thu Apr  4 18:31:58 2013
From: romain at r-enthusiasts.com (Romain Francois)
Date: Thu, 04 Apr 2013 18:31:58 +0200
Subject: [Rcpp-devel] Module with vector of a class with inheritance,
 how to avoid slicing
In-Reply-To: <1697171219.6781389.1365091852843.JavaMail.root@mines-paristech.fr>
References: <1697171219.6781389.1365091852843.JavaMail.root@mines-paristech.fr>
